title: Pumpkin weighing 1,969 pounds takes plumpest pumpkin title in San Francisco Bay Area contest
text:
Pumpkin weighing 1,969 pounds takes plumpest pumpkin title in San Francisco Bay Area contest 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
A rippled white whopper weighing in at 1,969 pounds took the title Monday for plumpest pumpkin at an annual San Francisco Bay Area contest....
